### Warranty API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 1. Create Warranty
POST {{baseUrl}}/warranties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standard Warranty",
  "description": "Covers manufacturing defects",
  "duration": 12,
  "durationUnit": "months"
}

### 2. Get Warranties (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/warranties
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Search by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/warranties?search=standard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/warranties?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Update Warranty
PUT {{baseUrl}}/warranties/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated coverage",
  "duration": 24,
  "durationUnit": "months"
}

### 6. Delete Warranty (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/warranties/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}